				Local Assets Folder
			</h3>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mt-4 lg:flex-row">
				<div class="lg:w-2/3">
					<p>Once the asset is saved, the .crp file will appear in the local assets folder:</p><p
						class="mt-4"
					>
						<span class="path">%LocalAppData%\Colossal Order\Cities_Skylines\Addons\Assets</span>
					</p><p class="mt-4">
						The AppData folder is hidden by default, you can access it by copying and pasting the path into
						the file explorer, or pressing <span class="key">Windows+R</span> and typing in appdata.
					</p>
				</div><div class="lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/images/shader/decal/decalcrp.jpeg" target="_blank">
						<Picture
							width={images.decalcrp.width / 2}
							densities={[1.5, 2]}
							formats={['avif', 'webp']}
							src={images.decalcrp}
							alt="CRP files in the local assets folder"
							class="w-full h-auto"
						/></a
					><p class="explanation">CRP files in the local assets folder.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<h2 class="pb-8 mt-24 text-4xl font-medium border-b-2 border-hit-gray-600 text-hit-gray-400" id="publish">
				Publish
			</h2>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mt-4 lg:flex-row">
				<div class="lg:w-2/3">
					<p>Once you have saved the asset and reloaded the game, you can publish the asset.</p><p
						class="mt-4"
					>
						Go to the content manager &gt; assets and find your asset, then click share.
					</p>
				</div><div class="lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/images/shader/decal/decalshare.jpeg" target="_blank">
						<Picture
							width={images.decalshare.width / 2}
							densities={[1.5, 2]}
							formats={['avif', 'webp']}
							src={images.decalshare}
							alt="Share button in content manager"
							class="w-full h-auto"
						/></a
					><p class="explanation">Share button in content manager.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<h3
				class="pb-4 mt-16 text-2xl font-semibold border-b text-hit-gray-400 border-hit-gray-500"
				id="title-and-description"
