				Update
			</h2>
			<p class="mt-4">
				To update your own item, you must subscribe to it first, then it will show up in the content manager. It
				won't be the same as a local asset, as it will show an "update" button.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4">
				When you click update, click the folder icon, and now you can change the Steam preview image and put
				your new asset in the content folder. If updating a pack, remember to put all the assets inside the
				content folder.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4">You can also add more assets to make it a bigger pack.</p>
