				<div class="lg:w-2/3">
					<p>This is not something you can change.</p><p class="mt-4">
						It's the hidden internal name used to refer to your asset in savefiles.
					</p><p class="mt-4">
						It's the reason why a local asset is not the same as a workshop published asset.
					</p><p class="mt-4">
						For local assets: filename.Asset Name_Data<br />For published workshop assets: SteamID.Asset
						Name_Data
					</p>
				</div><div class="lg:w-1/3">
